  "3133020": {
    "name": "浪漫满地",
    "steam_appid": 3133020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/7c617280d3a3066b33a2fa50feba8a0b.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=101 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/097fecf7e7150f034b191b514865498d.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/097fecf7e7150f034b191b514865498d.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Cozyrama里，你可以随意创造一个你认为的完美的世界。打磨形状，选择合适的颜色，享受装饰的乐趣。是建造一个温馨的村庄，还是打造一个色彩缤纷的花园？选择权在你手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/017743ec05f60dedb1134c34bbc91a42.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=101 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/36dbf8bff3ef3ec35e9d5fbac55e5390.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/36dbf8bff3ef3ec35e9d5fbac55e5390.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有时间限制，也没有玩家竞争。你要做的是享受一个美丽而充满想象力的世界，就像温暖的拥抱。可爱的动物四处游荡，如果你喜欢，还可以抚摸它们。无论几分钟还是几个小时，这里都是你放松身心的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/80db0ccd1ed657929538bd320cb9c6ce.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=101 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/5eca25c8e585737903f3f73944aa0174.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/5eca25c8e585737903f3f73944aa0174.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您还可以设计和装饰画中的世界。添加灯笼、长椅和小动物等装饰，让周围环境充满生机。无论您喜欢明亮活泼的空间，还是宁静繁星的夜晚，这个世界都由您来塑造。这里是宁静的绿洲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/139b58a3ea71fc468a067d43752f9ded.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=101 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/c71331272207972a16eaa78bc1d1c8c8.poster.avif?t=1765878706\" width=1170 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133020/extras/c71331272207972a16eaa78bc1d1c8c8.webm?t=1765878706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 内置超过 900 种物品，帮你打造完美场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 使用游戏内置的物品编辑器，从零开始创建定制装饰物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 通过 mod.io 与其他玩家分享你的场景和物品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 使用拍照模式拍摄精美截图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
